channel.title: How Often Boolean Process is Called
channel.description:
Alright, I set a timer to test this because I had a feeling it wasnt 500 milliseconds (half a second).
After Testing a few times, my average number came out to:
Boolean Process Is Being Called 176-180 Times Per Minute
I thought this might be useful for some people.
